## ğŸ§  Project Overview

**StandDown** is a Ribbon-powered platform designed to help teams reduce redundant stand-up meetings by replacing them with asynchronous, structured check-ins. 

Project managers and coordinators can use StandDown to send Ribbon-style interviews to employees â€” short, direct, and async. Team members answer questions on their own time, and their responses are analyzed with generative AI to surface key insights. 

Whether a manager wants detailed responses or just a quick summary of the overall team mood, StandDown delivers it â€” no calendar invites required.

